0further%20fueled%20the%20demand%20for%20engineers%20across%20industries.%20There%20is%20a%20high%20demand%20for%20skilled%20engineers%20in%20IT%2C%20manufacturing%2C%20construction%2C%20and%20infrastructure%20development%20owing%2C%20thanks%20to%20India's%20fast-growing%20economy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%C2%A0Kunal%20Shah%2C%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20(CEO)%20of%20fintech%20company%20CRED%2C%20stirred%20a%20debate%20on%20X%20by%20saying%20that%20''Engineers%20may%20eat%20doctor's%20jobs.''%C2%A0Mr%20Shah's%20statement%20likely%20comes%20as%20a%20reaction%20to%20the%20many%20recent%20technological%20advancements%20and%20engineers%20being%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20these%20inventions.%20Needless%20to%20say%2C%20emerging%20technologies%2C%20such%20as%20industrial%20robots%2C%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20and%20machine%20learning%2C%20are%20advancing%20at%20a%20rapid%20pace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20tweet%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EEngineers%20may%20eat%20doctor's%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Kunal%20Shah%20(%40kunalb11)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkunalb11%2Fstatus%2F1794350813076496816%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2025%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnSince%20being%20shared%2C%20this%20one-liner%20has%20garnered%20more%20than%206%2C50%2C000%20views%2C%203%2C200%20likes%20and%20more%20than%20600%20comments.%20Mr%20Shah's%20opinion%20has%20triggered%20a%20lively%20debate%20in%20the%20comment%20section%2C%20with%20X%20users%20sharing%20an%20array%20of%20reactions%20and%20comments.%20While%20some%20agreed%20with%20the%C2%A0entrepreneur's%20thought%2C%20noting%20how%20AI%20and%20diagnostics%20are%20increasingly%20being%20used%20in%20medicine%20and%20surgery%2C%20others%20emphasised%20the%20value%20of%20doctors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20user%20wrote%2C%20''Engineers%20will%20replace%20all%20the%20jobs%20in%20the%20world%20including%20sports%20in%20the%20next%20two%20decades.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20commented%2C%20''Unlikely.%20The%20hard%20part%20of%20medicine%20isn't%20applying%20known%20techniques%2C%20but%20dealing%20with%20the%20unknown%20and%20uniquely%20human.%20An%20AI%20might%20determine%20the%20best%20antibiotic%2C%20but%20it%20takes%20a%20doctor%20to%20convince%20the%20stubborn%20patient%20to%20take%20it%2C%20or%20notice%20subtle%20signs%20that%20something%20deeper%20is%20wrong.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20said%2C%20''Currently%2C%20engineers%20are%20consuming%20the%20entire%20corporate%20budget%20allocated%20for%20all%20employees%20in%20terms%20of%20salaries.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fourth%20disagreed%20saying%2C%20''Unlikely.%20The%20machine%20can't%20operate%20without%20doctors.''%20A%20fifth%20added%2C%20''With%20AI%20for%20sure.%20It's%20gonna%20be%20so%20interesting%20to%20see%20how%20the%20job%20landscape%20will%20change%20in%20the%20upcoming%20years.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20make%20any%20predictions%2C%20but%20I'm%20excited.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Kunal%20Shah%20is%20an%20angel%20investor%2C%20entrepreneur%20and%20founder%20of%20fintech%20company%20CRED%20and%20Freecharge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Carticle%20data-testid%3D%5C%22tweet%5C%22%20tabindex%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%3C%2Farticle%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716785880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2Ft5rsrqfo_kunal-shah_625x300_27_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fcred-ceo-kunal-shah-says-engineers-may-eat-doctors-jobs-triggers-debate-on-x-5754084%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20some%20agreed%20with%20him%2C%20noting%20how%20AI%20and%20diagnostics%20are%20increasingly%20being%20used%20in%20medicine%20and%20surgery%2C%20others%20emphasised%20the%20value%20of%20doctors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22en