nformation%20about%20the%20incident%20from%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20directed%20strong%20action%20against%20the%20culprits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20Mahendra%20Prasad)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716785820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fihk7lr1o_gujarat-newly-wed_625x300_27_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgujarat-gaming-zone-fire-newly-married-couple-among-27-killed-in-rajkot-gaming-zone-fire-5753832%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20newly%20married%20couple%20was%20among%20the%2027%20people%20killed%20in%20a%20massive%20fire%20at%20a%20gaming%20zone%20in%20Gujarat's%20Rajkot%20on%20Saturday%20evening.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgujarat-gaming-zone-fire-newly-married-couple-among-27-killed-in-rajkot-gaming-zone-fire-5753832%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgujarat-gaming-zone-fire-newly-married-couple-among-27-killed-in-rajkot-gaming-zone-fire-5753832%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgujarat-gaming-zone-fire-newly-married-couple-among-27-killed-in-rajkot-gaming-zone-fire-5753832%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Forensic%20Head%20Among%202%20Arrested%20For%20Manipulating%20Porsche%20Teen's%20Blood%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20latest%20twist%20in%20the%20Pune%20Porsche%20horror%2C%20two%20doctors%20have%20been%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20manipulating%20the%20blood%20test%20report%20of%20the%2017-year-old%2C%20whose%20late%20night%20drunk%20drive%20left%20two%2024-year-old%20software%20engineers%20dead%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Ajay%20Tawade%20and%20Dr%20Hari%20Harnor%20of%20Sasoon%20Hospital%20have%20been%20arrested%20by%20the%20Pune%20Crime%20Branch%2C%20which%20is%20investigating%20the%20case%20that%20has%20sparked%20nationwide%20outrage.%20Dr%20Tawade%20is%20head%20of%20the%20forensic%20lab%20at%20the%20state-run%20hospital%20in%20Pune.%20The%20phones%20of%C2%A0both%20doctors%20have%20been%20seized.%20Investigation%20has%20revealed%20Dr%20Tawade%20and%20the%20teen%20accused's%20father%20spoke%20over%20the%20phone%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20accident%2C%20according%20to%20police%20sources.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20reports%20had%20claimed%20that%20the%20Pune%20teen%2C%20who%20is%20now%20at%20an%20observation%20home%2C%20had%20tested%20negative%20for%20alcohol.%20However%2C%20CCTV%20footage%20from%20one%20of%20the%20bars%20he%20visited%20that%20night%20showed%20him%20drinking%20with%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPune%20Police%20Commissioner%20Amitesh%20Kumar%20earlier%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20case%20is%20not%20about%20an%20accident%20in%20which%20a%20mistake%20happened%20under%20the%20influence%20of%20alcohol%20and%20people%20died.%20Our%20case%20is%20that%20he%20had%20full%20knowledge%20that%20his%20conduct...%20he%20parties%20in%20two%20bars%2C%20rashly%20drives%20a%20car%20without%20a%20number%20plate%20on%20a%20narrow%2C%20congested%20street.%20He%20was%20fully%20in%20his%20senses%2C%20and%20he%20knew%20that%20people%20may%20die%20because%20of%20his%20actions.%26quot%3B%20The%20city%20police%20chief%20also%20said%20that%20two%20samples%20of%20the%20teen%20accused's%20blood%20were%20tested%20at%20different%20times%20after%20the%20accident%20to%20ensure%20accurate%20results.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%20sources%2C%20the%20first%20blood%20sample%20had%20no%20alcohol%2C%20but%20the%20second%20did.%20This%20raised%20suspicions%20and%20a%20DNA%20test%20was%20conducted.%20The%20DNA%20test%20revealed%20the%20samples%20were%20from%20different%20people%2C%20meaning%20that%20the%20minor's%20blood%20sample%20was%20switched%20with%20that%20of%20another%20person%20to%20ensure%20that%20his%20report%20did%20not%20mention%20alcohol.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teen%20belongs%20to%20a%20prominent%20realtor's%20family%20and%20it%20is%20alleged%20that%20his%20father%20and%20grandfather%20tried%20to%20influence%20the%20legal%20process%20to%20shield%20him.%20The%20teen's%20father%20has%20been%20arrested%20under%20charges%20of%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Act.%20His%20grandfather%20has%20also%20been%20arrested%20after%20the%20family's%20driver%20alleged%20that%20he%20was%20confined%20at%20the%20family's%20home%2C%20threatened%20and%20asked%20to%20take%20the%20blame%20for%20the%20accident.%20The%20other%20arrests%20in%20the%20case%20include%20staff%20of%20the%20two%20bars%20the%20teen%20visited%20that%20night.%20The%20doctors'%20arrest%20and%20allegations%20of%20manipulation%20of%20blood%20samples%20further%20strengthens%20the%20charge%20that%20the%20family%20blatantly%20used%20money%20and%20influence%20to%20protect%20the%20teen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20engineers%20--%20Ashwini%20Kostha%20and%20Anish%20Awadhiya%20--%20were%20on%20the%20bike%20when%20the%20Porsche%20hit%20their%20bike%20from%20behind.%20They%20died%20on%20the%20spot.%20The%20boy%20was%20granted%20bail%20within%2015%20hours%20of%20the%20accident%20on%20conditions%20seen%20as%20flimsy.%20He%20was%20asked%20to%20write%20a%20300-word%20essay%20on%20road%20accidents%2C%20told%20to%20work%20with%20traffic%20cops%20for%2015%20days%20and%20seek%20counselling%20for%20his%20drinking%20habit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20nationwide%20outrage%2C%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20later%20modified%20the%20order%20and%20sent%20him%20to%20the%20observation%20home.%20The%20police%20have%20urged%20the%20board%20for%20permission%20to%20try%20the%20teen%20accused%20--%20aged%2017%20years%20and%20eight%20months%20--%20as%20an%20adult.%20The%20matter%20is%20currently%20being%20examined.%C2%A0The%20families%20of%20the%20two%20engineers%20have%20said%20this%20is%20%26quot%3Bmurder%2C%20not%20accident%26quot%3B%20and%20sought%20stringent%20punishment%20for%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716785820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fo4gv874g_porsche-split_625x300_27_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-doctors-arrested-for-manipulating-blood-test-report-of-pune-teen-who-ran-over-2-techies-with-porsche-say-sources-5753624%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20doctors%20have%20been%20arrested%20for%20manipulating%20the%20blood%20test%20report%20of%20the%2017-year-old%20boy%20who%20ran%20over%20two%20techies%20in%20Pune%20in%20a%20late-night%20drunken%20dash%20in%20a%20Porsche%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-doctors-arrested-for-manipulating-blood-test-report-of-pune-teen-who-ran-over-2-techies-with-porsche-say-sources-5753624%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-doctors-arrested-for-manipulating-blood-test-report-of-pune-teen-who-ran-over-2-techies-with-porsche-say-sources-5753624%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-doctors-arrested-for-manipulating-blood-test-report-of-pune-teen-who-ran-over-2-techies-with-porsche-say-sources-5753624%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22VIDEO%3A%20SRK%20joins%20fans%20and%20chants%20'CSK'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716785353000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110453206%2Cimgsize-74076.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshah-rukh-khan-wins-the-internet-as-he-joins-fans-and-chants-csk-at-the-stadium-despite-kkrs-win-watch-video%2Farticleshow%2F110452975.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F110452975.cms%5C%22