ng%20up%20for%20stalwarts%20like%20Narine%2C%20Russell%20and%20Starc%20and%20also%20contribute%20their%20share%20in%20the%20team's%20win.%20That's%20how%20a%20team%20wins%20the%20IPL.%20We%20have%20seen%20this%20over%20the%20years.%20It's%20not%20the%20Orange%20Cap%20that%20wins%20you%20the%20IPL%20but%20it%20is%20the%20contributions%20like%20300%20runs%20each%20(of%20many%20players)%2C%26quot%3B%20Rayudu%20said%20in%20a%20chat%20on%20Star%20Sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20the%20orange%20cap%20that%20wins%20you%20ipl%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F7bW16z29k3%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F7bW16z29k3%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Manojkumar%20(%40Manojkumar_099)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FManojkumar_099%2Fstatus%2F1794798371561173481%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2026%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ERayudu%20even%20suggested%20that%20Virat%20should%20lower%20his%20standards%20as%20other%20batters%20in%20the%20team%20feel%20pressured%20string%20to%20match%20the%20contributions%20of%20the%20India%20great.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20stalwart%20and%20a%20legend%20there%20in%20the%20team.%20He%20sets%20so%20high%20standards%20which%20puts%20pressure%20on%20the%20youngsters%20to%20emulate%20him.%20So%2C%20Virat%20needs%20to%20lower%20his%20standards%20a%20bit%20so%20that%20the%20youngsters%20can%20be%20in%20a%20good%20state%20of%20mind%20in%20the%20dressing%20room%2C%26quot%3B%20Rayudu%20stressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20a%20few%20days%20ago%2C%20Rayudu%20called%20out%20the%20poor%20management%20by%20RCB's%20bosses%2C%20saying%20they%20prefer%20individual%