lifts-the-ipl-trophy%2Farticleshow%2F110449783.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20Hospital%20Where%207%20Babies%20Died%20In%20Huge%20Fire%20Is%20Not%20New%20To%20Controversy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20children's%20hospital%2C%20where%20seven%20babies%20died%20in%20a%20massive%20fire%20on%20Saturday%20night%2C%20was%20embroiled%20in%20a%20massive%20controversy%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20over%20the%20assault%20of%20a%20newborn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20staff%20of%20Baby%20Care%20New%20Born%20Hospital%20in%20East%20Delhi's%20Vivek%20Vihar%20was%20accused%20of%20assaulting%20a%20baby%20during%20treatment%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20was%20registered%20after%20a%20security%20camera%20footage%20-%20which%20had%20gone%20viral%20-%20showed%20a%20nurse%20beating%20the%20baby%20due%20to%20which%20the%20boy's%20hand%20was%20fractured.%20The%20First%20Information%20Report%20or%20FIR%20had%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20hospital%20was%20unregistered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday's%20tragedy%20has%20revealed%20several%20lapses%20at%20the%20hospital%20yet%20again.%20The%20facility%20didn't%20have%20any%20fire%20extinguishers%20or%20an%20emergency%20exit%2C%20police%20said.%20The%20doctor%20who%20was%20on%20duty%20when%20the%20accident%20happened%20was%20not%20qualified%20to%20treat%20newborns%20in%20need%20of%20neo-natal%20incentive%20care%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(Shahdara)%20Surendra%20Chaudhary%20said%20that%20the%20hospital%20had%20more%20than%20the%20authorised%20number%20of%20oxygen%20cylinders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20licence%20issued%20to%20the%20hospital%20by%20the%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Health%20Services%20or%20DGHS%20had%20already%20expired%20on%20March%2031%2C%20nearly%20two%20months%20before%20the%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Naveen%20Khichi%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20hospital%20who%20had%20been%20on%20the%20run%20since%20Saturday%20night%20after%20the%20fire%20broke%20out%2C%20was%20arrested%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Naveen%2C%20who%20runs%20many%20other%20hospitals%20for%20babies%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20is%20being%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20doctor%20who%20was%20on%20duty%20when%20the%20fire%20broke%20out%20has%20also%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fire%20tore%20through%20Baby%20Care%20New%20Born%20Hospital%20on%20Saturday%20night%20in%20which%20seven%20newborns%20were%20killed.%20The%20fire%2C%20which%20erupted%20around%2011.32%20pm%2C%20quickly%20intensified%20due%20to%20the%20presence%20of%20numerous%20oxygen%20cylinders%20that%20began%20to%20explode%2C%20spreading%20the%20blaze%20further%20and%20causing%20extensive%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20who%20saw%20the%20huge%20fire%20engulf%20the%20children's%20hospital%20had%20scaled%20the%20compound%20wall%2C%20and%20climbed%20from%20the%20rear%20side%20of%20the%20building%20to%20rescue%20newborns%2C%20eyewitnesses%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20local%20residents%20and%20members%20of%20a%20non-profit%2C%20Shaheed%20Seva%20Dal%2C%20were%20the%20first%20to%20rush%20to%20help.%20They%20were%20soon%20joined%20by%20fire%20department%20officials%20and%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716777180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F2eer67oo_delhi-hospital-fire-new_625x300_26_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-children-hospital-fire-naveen-khichi-newborns-killed-in-fire-baby-care-new-born-hospital-delhi-hospital-where-7-babies-died-in-huge-fire-is-not-5753393%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20children's%20hospital%2C%20where%20seven%20babies%20died%20in%20a%20massive%20fire%20yesterday%2C%20was%20embroiled%20in%20a%20massive%20controversy%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20over%20the%20assault%20of%20a%20newborn.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22