20lift%20its%20third%20IPL%20trophy%20on%20Sunday.%20The%20likes%20of%20Andre%20Russell%20and%20Harshit%20Rana%20found%20it%20tough%20to%20describe%20the%20feeling%20of%20being%20IPL%20champions%2C%20even%20as%20they%20praised%20Nayar.%20KKR%20crushed%20Hyderabad%20by%20eight%20wickets%20in%20a%20completely%20one-sided%20final%20after%20bowling%20out%20their%20opponents%20for%20113%2C%20the%20lowest%20ever%20total%20in%20an%20IPL%20title%20clash.%20This%20was%20KKR's%20third%20IPL%20title.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20cannot%20tell%20how%20happy%20I%20am%2C%26quot%3B%20Harshit%2C%20who%20picked%20up%20two%20wickets%20in%20the%20final%2C%20said%20after%20the%20triumph.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20seasoned%20Russell%20was%20lost%20for%20words%20as%20he%20tried%20to%20hold%20back%20his%20tears.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20words%20to%20describe.%20It%20means%20so%20much.%20I%20am%20happy%20that%20all%20of%20us%20were%20very%20disciplined%20and%20worked%20towards%20one%20goal.%20This%20franchise%20has%20done%20a%20lot%20for%20me.%20It's%20a%20big%20gift%20from%20all%20of%20us%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Russell%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVarun%20Chakravarathy%2C%20who%20has%20had%20a%20successful%20season%20with%20his%20spin%20bowling%2C%20lauded%20Nayar's%20contributions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20I%20can%20think%20right%20now%20is%20of%20the%20person%20who%20built%20this%20Indian%20core%3A%20Abhishek%20Nayar.%20'Please%20come%20here'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20asking%20the%20former%20Mumbai%20batter%20to%20join%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVenkatesh%20Iyer%2C%20who%20remained%20not%20out%20on%2052%20off%2026%20balls%20in%20an%20easy%20chase%20of%20114%2C%20also%20mentioned%20Nayar's%20role%20in%20the%20team's%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReally%20happy%20with%20it.%20As%20Varun%20mentioned%2C%20Abhishek%20Nayar%20deserves%20all%20the%20credit%20in%20the%20world.%20Some%20contributions%20go%20unnoticed%2C%20I%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20they%20don't.%20This%20guy%20deserves%20all%20the%20credit%20in%20the%20world%20for%20the%20way%20he%20has%20been%20working%20for%20this%20franchise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20win%20is%20for%20the%20fans%20who%20turned%20up%20year%20after%20year%20and%20waited%20for%2010%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Venkatesh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20lost%20the%20toss%2C%20KKR%20produced%20a%20clinical%20effort%20with%20the%20ball%20to%20dismiss%20SRH%20for%20113%2C%20the%20lowest%20ever%20total%20in%20an%20IPL%20title%20clash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKKR%20chased%20down%20the%20target%20of%20114%20with%20as%20many%20as%2057%20balls%20to%20spare%2C%20even%20as%20team%20mentor%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20and%20head%20coach%20Chandrakant%20Pandit%20watched%20the%20action%20unfolding%20in%20the%20middle%20from%20the%20dugout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20share%20one%20short%20story%20that%20when%20GG%20bhaiya%20was%20named%20the%20mentor.%20I%20sent%20him%20a%20long%20message%20as%20I%20was%20really%20happy.%20But%20he%20replied%20saying%2C%20'Thank%20you%20but%20I%20would%20be%20happy%20if%20we%20stand%20at%20the%20podium%20with%20the%20trophy%20in%20our%20hands'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20is%20that%20day%20and%20I%20will%20never%20forget%20that%20message%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nitish%20Rana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeamer%20Vaibhav%20Arora%2C%20who%20bowled%20a%20beautiful%20delivery%20to%20dismiss%20the%20dangerous%20Travis%20Head%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20role%20is%20to%20take%20wickets%20with%20the%20new%20ball.%20After%20that%20the%20spinners%20were%20doing%20their%20jobs.%20So%2C%20today%20also%20the%20aim%20was%20to%20take%20wickets%20in%20the%20powerplay%2C%20which%20happened%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%20Rinku%20Singh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20dream%20of%20seven%20years%20is%20complete.%20Finally%20I%20will%20lift%20the%20trophy.%20I%20am%20proud%20of%20my%20whole%20team%20and%20GG%20sir.%20It%20was%20God's%20plan.%26quot%3B%20KKR's%20bowling%20coach%20Bharat%20Arun%2C%20whose%20behind-the-scenes%20nous%20played%20such%20a%20huge%20part%20in%20India%20becoming%20the%20world's%20best%20Test%20side%2C%20praised%20the%20KKR%20players%20for%20their%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20was%20pretty%20tough%2C%20the%20last%20two%20years.%20It%20was%20touch%20and%20go%20-%20we%20didn't%20qualify.%20It%20needed%20a%20lot%20of%20introspection%20and%20now%20we%20can%20savour%20this%20moment.%26quot%3B%20When%20asked%20about%20Player%20of%20the%20Final%20Mitchell%20Starc%2C%20Arun%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20Mitch%20coming%20into%20the%20team%20boosted%20the%20confidence%20of%20other%20youngsters%20in%20the%20side.%20He%20is%20probably%20the%20best%20bowler%20in%20the%20world.%20Once%20he%20understood%20the%20Indian%20conditions%2C%20he%20was%20excellent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSpinners%20mature%20with%20age%2C%20and%20with%20Sunny%20(Sunil%20Narine)%20and%20Varun%20bowling%20in%20tandem%2C%20it%20was%20superb.%26quot%3B%20Speaking%20about%20Narine%20the%20batter%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20brought%20a%20totally%20different%20dimension%20to%20our%20batting.%20It%20was%20Gautam%20who%20insisted%20that%20he%20opened%20and%20it%20paid%20dividends.%20It's%20a%20great%20night%20and%20now%20it's%20time%20to%20celebrate.%26quot%3B%20PTI%20AH%20AH%20UNG%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716774900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F3dth80u8_a_625x300_27_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fnot-gautam-gambhir-kkr-star-credits-this-ex-india-player-for-teams-indian-core-5751965%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20players%20highlighted%20the%20contributions%20of%20mentor%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20and%20assistant%20co