%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaza's%20civil%20defence%20agency%20said%20Israeli%20strikes%20killed%20and%20wounded%20at%20least%2050%20people%20in%20the%20area%2C%20where%20it%20said%20100%2C000%20displaced%20people%20live.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20said%20Palestinians%20must%20%26quot%3Brise%20up%20and%20march%26quot%3B%20against%20the%20Israeli%20army's%20%26quot%3Bmassacre%26quot%3B%20in%20Rafah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Strong%20Palestinian%20Authority'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20vowed%20to%20pursue%20the%20offensive%20ahead%20of%20a%20war%20cabinet%20meeting%20amid%20intense%20diplomacy%20to%20forge%20a%20truce%20and%20a%20hostage-release%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20long%20rejected%20Hamas's%20demand%20for%20a%20permanent%20end%20to%20the%20conflict%20triggered%20by%20the%20Palestinian%20Hamas%20group's%20October%207%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20Israeli%20official%2C%20speaking%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%2C%20told%20AFP%20the%20war%20cabinet%20would%20%26quot%3Bdiscuss%20a%20hostage%20release%20deal%26quot%3B%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20meeting%2C%20Netanyahu's%20office%20said%20Hamas's%20chief%20in%20Gaza%2C%20Yahya%20Sinwar%2C%20%26quot%3Bcontinues%20to%20demand%20the%20end%20of%20the%20war%2C%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20IDF%20(army)%20from%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20and%20leaving%20Hamas%20in%20place%2C%20so%20that%20it%20will%20be%20able%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20atrocities%20of%20October%207%20again%20and%20again%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrime%20Minister%20Netanyahu%20strongly%20opposes%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEU%20members%20Ireland%20and%20Spain%2C%20and%20also%20Norway%2C%20have%20said%20they%20will%20recognise%20the%20State%20of%20Palestine%20from%20Tuesday%2C%20drawing%20furious%20Israeli%20condemnation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20order%20to%20make%20peace%2C%20we%20need%20a%20strong%20Palestinian%20Authority%2C%20not%20a%20weaker%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20EU's%20foreign%20policy%20chief%20Josep%20Borrell%2C%20who%20met%20in%20Brussels%20with%20Palestinian%20prime%20minister%20Mohammed%20Mustafa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMustafa%2C%20whose%20government%20is%20based%20in%20the%20occupied%20West%20Bank%2C%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bfirst%20priority%26quot%3B%20was%20to%20support%20the%20people%20in%20Gaza%2C%20especially%20through%20a%20ceasefire%2C%20and%20then%20%26quot%3Brebuilding%20the%20institutions%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20territory%20after%20Hamas%20seized%20it%20from%20the%20PA%20in%202007.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20has%20pushed%20for%20renewed%20international%20efforts%20to%20halt%20the%20war%2C%20now%20in%20its%20eighth%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20official%20had%20said%20Saturday%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20an%20intention%20to%20renew%20these%20talks%20this%20week%26quot%3B%20after%20negotiations%20involving%20US%2C%20Qatari%20and%20Egyptian%20mediators%20stalled%20in%20early%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPressure%20on%20Israel%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20October%207%20attack%20on%20southern%20Israel%20resulted%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%20more%20than%201%2C170%20people%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20according%20to%20an%20AFP%20tally%20based%20on%20Israeli%20official%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20operatives%20also%20took%20252%20hostages%2C%20121%20of%20whom%20remain%20in%20Gaza%2C%20including%2037%20the%20army%20says%20are%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20retaliatory%20offensive%20has%20killed%20at%20least%2035%2C984%20people%20in%20Gaza%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Hamas-run%20territory's%20health%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20war%20grinds%20on%2C%20the%20families%20of%20hostages%20still%20held%20by%20operatives%20have%20piled%20pressure%20on%20Netanyahu%20to%20secure%20a%20deal%20to%20free%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWashington%20has%20also%20taken%20a%20tougher%20line%20with%20its%20close%20ally%20as%20outrage%20over%20the%20war%20and%20US%20support%20for%20Israel%20has%20become%20a%20major%20issue%20for%20Biden%2C%20seeking%20re-election%20in%20a%20battle%20against%20Donald%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStrikes%20on%20Tel%20Aviv%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas's%20armed%20wing%20said%20Sunday%20that%20it%20targeted%20Tel%20Aviv%20%26quot%3Bwith%20a%20large%20rocket%20barrage%20in%20response%20to%20the%20Zionist%20massacres%20against%20civilians%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHamas%20launched%20these%20rockets%20from%20near%20two%20mosques%20in%20Rafah%2C%26quot%3B%20Israeli%20military%20spokesman%20Rear%20Admiral%20Daniel%20Hagari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHamas%20is%20holding%20our%20hostages%20in%20Rafah%2C%20which%20is%20why%20we%20have%20been%20conducting%20a%20precise%20operation%26quot%3B%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20Nations%20has%20warned%20of%20looming%20famine%20in%20besieged%20Gaza%2C%20where%20most%20hospitals%20are%20no%20longer%20functioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20Monday%2C%20the%20prosecutor%20at%20the%20International%20Criminal%20Court%20said%20he%20was%20seeking%20arrest%20warrants%20for%20Netanyahu%20and%20his%20defence%20minister%20as%20well%20as%20for%20three%20top%20Hamas%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20ordered%20Israel%20to%20halt%20its%20Rafah%20offensive%20or%20any%20other%20operation%20there%20that%20could%20bring%20about%20%26quot%3Bthe%20physical%20destruction%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716773400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fb5t4bgjo_rafah-reuters_625x300_27_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld