tions%20in%20air%2C%20rail%20and%20road%20transportation%20in%20Kolkata%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20southern%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Eastern%20and%20South%20Eastern%20Railways%20cancelled%20some%20trains%2C%20and%20the%20Kolkata%20airport%20suspended%20flight%20operations%20for%2021%20hours%2C%20affecting%20394%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Syama%20Prasad%20Mookerjee%20Port%20in%20Kolkata%20has%20also%20suspended%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Coast%20Guard%20(ICG)%20ensured%20no%20loss%20of%20life%20or%20property%20at%20sea%2C%20with%20remote%20operating%20stations%20alerting%20vessels%20and%20ships.%20Nine%20disaster%20relief%20teams%20were%20on%20standby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Navy%20has%20readied%20two%20ships%20equipped%20with%20Humanitarian%20Assistance%20and%20Disaster%20Relief%20(HADR)%20and%20medical%20supplies%2C%20with%20aviation%20assets%20on%20standby%20for%20rapid%20response.%20Specialised%20diving%20teams%20and%20flood%20relief%20teams%20have%20also%20been%20prepared%20for%20deployment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716758880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fne1cmu78_cyclone-remal-kolkata_625x300_27_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcyclone-remal-makes-landfall-on-bengal-coast-leaves-trail-of-destruction-5752621%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20winds%20gusting%20up%20to%20135%20kilometres%20per%20hour%2C%20severe%20cyclonic%20storm%20'Remal'%20made%20landfall%20between%20the%20coasts%20of%20Bangladesh%20and%20adjoining%20West%20Bengal%2C%20bringing%20heavy%20rains%20that%20flooded%20homes%20and%20farmland%2C%20and%20leaving%20a%20trail%20of%20destruction.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3