.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20used%20to%20work%20at%20Google%2C%20people%20would%20always%20submit%20artistic%20resumes%20with%20charts%20and%20the%20Google%20colours%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Fackrell%20said.%20Instead%20of%20writing%20a%20list%20of%20titles%20and%20accomplishments%2C%20they'd%20split%20their%20resume%20into%20columns%20and%20quadrants.%20Ms%20Fackrell%20believes%20that%20by%20creating%20these%20colourful%20resumes%2C%20%26quot%3Byou're%20just%20being%20a%20little%20gimmicky%26quot%3B.%20Some%20of%20these%20resumes%20are%20also%20%26quot%3Bnot%20easily%20readable%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20makes%20the%20applicants'%20qualifications%20harder%20to%20discern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Fackrell%20has%20worked%20with%20Google%2C%20Apple%2C%20Nvidia%2C%20and%20Samsung.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20an%20ideal%20resume%20should%20be%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20resume%20is%20showcasing%20you%20in%20a%2010-to-60-second%20format%20on%20paper.%26quot%3B%20Telling%20a%20compelling%20story%20and%20being%20as%20clear%20and%20concise%20as%20possible%20%26quot%3Bis%20what's%20going%20to%20win%20you%20in%20a%20sea%26quot%3B%20of%20other%20applicants%2C%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20while%20listing%20powerful%20accomplishments%2C%20the%20document%20must%20not%20be%20more%20than%20two%20pages%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20aesthetics%2C%20Ms%20Fackrell%20identifies%20another%20red%20flag%3A%20resumes%20that%20simply%20list%20daily%20tasks.%20%26quot%3BWhere%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20make%20mistakes%20on%20their%20resume%20is%20they're%20listing%20out%20their%20daily%20job%20duties%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20publication.%20%C2%A0Instead%2C%20your%20resume%20should%20be%20a%20showcase%20of%20accomplishments%2C%20woven%20together%20with%20relevant%20job%20duties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecruiters%20aren't%20interested%20in%20your%20daily%20grind%20of%20emails%20and%20meetings.%20They%20want%20to%20see%20evidence%20of%20impactful%20project