%3A%22%E2%80%98It%20Heals%20Me%E2%80%99%3A%20How%20I%20Grow%20300%20Plants%20Including%2070%20Fruit%20Trees%20On%20My%20Terrace%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGardening%20is%20therapeutic%20for%20me.%20It%20healed%20and%20grounded%20me%2C%20and%20made%20me%20a%20better%20mother%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sushma%20Reddy%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2038-year-old%20encountered%20a%20major%20crisis%20six%20years%20back%20when%20her%20then%204-year-old%20son%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20ADHD%20(Attention-deficit%2Fhyperactivity%20disorder).%20The%20college%20topper%20and%20top%20performing%20software%20engineer%20had%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F266454%2Fhyderabad-engineer-mom-quits-job-disability-speech-delay-special-ed-teacher%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equit%20her%20thriving%20career%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20focus%20on%20what%20mattered%20the%20most%20at%20the%20time%20%E2%80%93%20her%20son.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20followed%20the%20diagnosis%20was%20shock%2C%20a%20sense%20of%20helplessness%20and%20a%20desire%20to%20provide%20the%20best%20for%20her%20child.%20Sushma%20would%20take%20him%20for%20therapy%20daily%20and%20wait%20outside%20for%20three%20hours%20of%20the%20appointment.%20A%20few%20months%20of%20this%20gruelling%20schedule%20left%20the%20Bengaluru%20resident%20drained%20both%20physically%20and%20mentally.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20felt%20depressed%2C%20lost%20interest%20in%20her%20daily%20activities%2C%20stopped%20eating%20well%2C%20which%20all%20led%20to%20weight%20loss%20as%20well.%20A%20gynaecologist%20told%20her%20that%20she%20must%20pick%20up%20a%20hobby%20and%20do%20something%20that%20interests%20her.%20This%20advice%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20life-changing%20one%2C%20which%20ignited%20a%20deep-rooted%20passion%20in%20her.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20decided%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20gardening%20as%20it%20would%20come%20with%20an%20added%20advantage%20of%20giving%20her%20son%20fresh%2C%20organic%20vegetables%20and%20fruits%20to%20eat.%20Starting%20with%20a%20money%20plant%20in%202018%2C%20the%20engineer%20slowly%20grew%20to%20realise%20that%20she%20had%20a%20green%20thumb.%20From%20indoor%20plants%2C%20she%20branched%20to%20vegetables%20and%20fruits%20on%20the%201%2C000%20square%20feet%20terrace%20of%20her%20rented%20apartment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20it%20has%20grown%20into%20a%20green%20haven%20with%20over%20300%20plants%2C%2070%20of%20which%20are%20fruit%20trees.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProviding%20Sushma%20with%20a%20much-needed%20outlet%20for%20her%20worries%2C%20she%20spends%20three%20hours%20a%20day%20tending%20to%20her%20darling%20plants%2C%20all%20on%20her%20own.%20Her%20passion%20also%20led%20to%20an%20Instagram%20account%20%40glitters.of.nature%20which%20has%20over%204%20lakh%20followers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20adds%20to%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F303953%2Fshashi-manchanda-homemaker-grows-organic-vegetables-flowers-on-terrace-garden-gurugram%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eterrace%20gardener%E2%80%99s%20feat%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20the%20fact%20that%20all%20her%20plants%2C%20including%20her%20fruit%20trees%20are%20grown%20on%2010-16%20inch%20pots!%20She%20shares%20her%20story%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20garden%2C%20and%20a%20home%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20Visakhapatnam%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Sushma%20moved%20to%20Bengaluru%20post%20marriage.%20When%20her%20son%20was%20born%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20the%20new%20parents%20started%20noticing%20some%20developmental%20delays%2C%20especially%20with%20regards%20to%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201920px)%20100vw%2C%201920px%5C%22%20