r%20his%20speech%20to%20develop%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sushma%20shares%3Cstrong%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20this%20continued%20till%20four%2C%20the%20concerned%20parents%20took%20him%20to%20different%20doctors%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20correct%20diagnosis%20of%20ADHD.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20he%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20autism%2Ca%20neurological%20condition%20that%20causes%20difficulty%20with%20social%20interaction%20and%20communication%2C%20at%20the%20NIMHANS%20(National%20Institute%20of%20Mental%20Health%20and%20Neurosciences)%2C%20she%20shares%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20therapy%20for%20the%20same.%20Over%20the%20next%20few%20years%2C%20he%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20ADHD%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20the%20mother.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20long%20therapy%20sessions%20and%20difficulty%20in%20communicating%20with%20her%20little%20one%20took%20a%20toll%20on%20the%20young%20mother%2C%20which%20subsequently%20led%20to%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347565%2Fgrow-mangoes-chikoo-fruits-on-trees-urban-gardener-jayanti-sahoo-terrace-gardening-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etaking%20up%20gardening%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSushma3-1715673958.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gardening%20is%20therapeutic%20for%20Sushma%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSushma3-1715673958.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSushma3-1715673958-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FSushma3-1715673958-500x666.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2