0tourism%20with%20agriculture%20but%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20quite%20put%20his%20finger%20on%20what%20this%20would%20be%3B%20until%20in%202008%2C%20an%20experience%20changed%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20may%20have%20heard%20of%20food%20scientist-turned-farmer%20Chandrasekhar%20Bhadsavle%20%E2%80%94%20famous%20for%20introducing%20the%20Saguna%20Rice%20Technique%20(SRT)%20among%20a%20handful%20of%20farmers%20in%20Neral%20(Karjat)%20in%202013%20and%20for%20championing%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20agro-tourism%20initiative%20%E2%80%98Saguna%20Baug%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20located%2075%20km%20from%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20degraded%20land%2C%20the%20Baug%20was%20transformed%20into%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F252647%2Fmango-farm-ultra-high-density-planting-uhdp-kesar-alphonso-profits-farmer-success-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethriving%20land%20with%20food%20crops%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20bamboo%2C%20livestock%20and%20fish%3B%20a%20space%20that%20promoted%20the%20surrounding%20wild%20biodiversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20day%20while%20on%20a%20drive%2C%20Ganesh%20came%20across%20Saguna%20Baug%20and%20having%20heard%20so%20much%20about%20the%20place%2C%20decided%20to%20stop%20by.%20They%20say%20some%20things%20can%20change%20your%20life%E2%80%99s%20trajectory%20completely.%20For%20Ganesh%2C%20a%20guided%20tour%20through%20the%20green%20space%20with%20Bhadsavle%E2%80%99s%20running%20commentary%20on%20how%20freeing%20nature%20could%20really%20be%20was%20one%20such%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20was%20all%20I%20needed%20to%20confirm%20my%20faith%20in%20an%20idea%20that%20I%20had%20had%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ganesh%2C%20adding%20that%20his%20vision%20finally%20got%20a%20name.%20He%20decided%20to%20build%20an%20agro-tourism%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhere%20mangoes%20play%20host%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minute%20you%20step%20into%20Ganesh%20Agro%20Tourism%20homestay%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20be%20able%20to%20tell%20the%20stark%20difference%20between%20the%20city%20air%20from%20the%20fresh%20gusts%20here.%20Mango%20trees%20move%20almost%20melodically%2C%20the%20branches%20causing%20a%20rustle%20that%20makes%20you%20stop%20and%20want%20to%20interpret.%20Watching%20these%20beauties%20and%20feasting%20on%20their%20fruits%20constitutes%20a%20great%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGanesh%20lets%20us%20in%20on%20the%20inception%20behind%20this%20homestay%20idea%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20once%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20packing%20unit.%20When%20we%20started%20getting%20so%20many%20guests%20visiting%20us%20to%20watch%20our%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332094%2Frajasthan-rubi-pareek-doubles-profit-with-organic-farming-gives-free-training%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorganic%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E%20practices%2C%20we%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20nice%20to%20create%20a%20place%20where%20they%20could%20stay.%20And%20so%20we%20decided%20to%20modify%20the%20packing%20unit%20into%20a%20homestay.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-3-1715947573.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20homestay%20is%20built%20in%20typical%20Maharashtrian%20style%20and%20is%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20paddy%20and%20mango%20plantations%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-3-1715947573.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-3-1715947573-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-3-1715947573-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%